DialogueNode.dialogue: Hey, Stan. How are you today?
That's good to hear... I think...
Could I ask you some questions?
Alright I'm going back to work now
Honestly I'm pretty busy right now
It's pretty important, Stan. I've received a report regarding gender discrimination in the office and would like to discuss this with you.
You are the supervisor, after all.
Gender discrimination? That's ludicrous. Who reported that?
So you haven't noticed any discriminatory or disrespectful behavior then?
It was an anonymous report, and I think there's validity in it. Are you sure you haven't noticed this at all?
I'm offended that you think you can just come in here and accuse me of running a workplace that's riddled with discrimination.
I won't discuss this with you again, Alex. I'm going back to work.
